{"id": "30102", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=30102", "title": "Feder\u00eego Aliz\u00earo", "text": "O Feder\u00eego Aliz\u00earo (d\u00eeto Aliz\u00eari asc\u00ec, Z\u00eana, 27 dex\u00e9nbre 1817 - Z\u00eana, 28 set\u00e9nbre 1882) o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to 'n st\u00f2rico, insegn\u00e0nte e leter\u00f2u zen\u00e9ize.\nV\u00ectta.\nO Feder\u00eego Aliz\u00earo o l'\u00e0 nasci\u00fbo a Z\u00eana a-i 27 de dex\u00e9nbre do 1817 da Gi\u00f6x\u00e8ppe e Gi\u00e0nca Grond\u00f3nn-a, seg\u00f3ndo de n\u00eauve fr\u00e6, inte 'na fam\u00ecggia de c\u00e2set\u00e6 abast\u00e0nsa r\u00eccca. O s'\u00e9 d\u00f3nca laore\u00f2u in l\u00e9zze, scib\u00e9n ch'o l'\u00e9 f\u00eeto pas\u00f2u a-a s\u00f2 pasci\u00f3n, a letiat\u00fba, mat\u00eaia inta qu\u00e6 o l'\u00e0 av\u00fbo c\u00f3mme m\u00e9istro o P\u00f2ulo Reb\u00f9ffo. O l'\u00e0 in prin\u00e7\u00ecpio travagi\u00f2u inte 'n setiman\u00e2le leter\u00e2io, l'\"Espero\", fond\u00f2u da l\u00ea e da \u00e2tri leter\u00e6 into 1840, co-o pr\u00ecmmo n\u00f9mero ch'o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to public\u00f2u a-i 5 de dex\u00e9nbre da l'edit\u00f4 Z\u00e2ne Bat\u00ecsta Fer\u00e0ndo. Inte qu\u00e9lli \u00e0nni, l\"'Espero\" o l'\u00eaa 'na publica\u00e7i\u00f3n abast\u00e0nsa avox\u00e2, ch'a cont\u00e2va in sci\u00e2 colabora\u00e7i\u00f3n de inport\u00e0nti studi\u00f4xi c\u00f3mme o P\u00eao Bernab\u00f2 Silor\u00e2ta e o Mich\u00ea Gi\u00f6x\u00e8ppe Can\u00e2. A \u00f2gni m\u00f2ddo qu\u00e9sta esperi\u00e9nsa a no l'\u00e9 du\u00e2 a l\u00f3ngo, apr\u00eauvo a-a sopresci\u00f3n do giorn\u00e2le, dec\u00eeza into 1845 pi-\u00e2 tend\u00e9nsa a trat\u00e2 i probl\u00eami da miz\u00eaia do p\u00f2polo, difond\u00e9ndo n\u00eauve in sc\u00ee n\u00eauvi az\u00eeli de l'\u00f2pera do Fer\u00e0nte Ap\u00f2rti, ch'a l'\u00e0iva alarm\u00f2u a poli\u00e7\u00eea, ch'a l'acuz\u00e2va o giorn\u00e2le de \"virol\u00e9nsa e bozit\u00e6\".\nTra i s\u00f2 pr\u00ecmmi scr\u00eeti, into 1839 l'Aliz\u00earo o l'\u00e0 public\u00f2u 'n'arecug\u00e9ita intitol\u00e2 \"I migliori monumenti sepolcrali in Liguria\", colabor\u00e0ndo inte l'\u00f2pera de gr\u00f9ppo, cu\u00e2 da-o Com\u00f9n pe l'eut\u00e9n congr\u00e8sso di scensi\u00e6 ch'o s'\u00eaa riun\u00eeo a Z\u00eana, intitol\u00e2 \"Descrizione di Genova e del Genovesato\", spart\u00eea inte tr\u00e9i vol\u00f9mmi e public\u00e2 into 1846. Inte qu\u00e9llo \u00e0nno o l'\u00e0 public\u00f2u a s\u00f2 \"Guida artistica per la citt\u00e0 di Genova\" asc\u00ec, gr\u00e0nde \u00f2pera inte tr\u00e9i vol\u00f9mmi che, a desp\u00eato da pez\u00e0nte pr\u00f6za t\u00ecpica de l'out\u00f4, a forn\u00eeva de informa\u00e7io\u00ecn menu\u00e7i\u00f4ze in sc\u00ea \u00f2pere conserv\u00e6 a Z\u00eana inte qu\u00e9llo per\u00eeodo. S'\u00e9 dedic\u00f2u asc\u00ec a de tradu\u00e7io\u00ecn, c\u00f3mme qu\u00e9lla, into 1852, do \"Della guerra di Spagna\". A qu\u00e9llo mom\u00e9nto rem\u00f3nta asc\u00ec 'na com\u00e9dia in\u00e9dita in v\u00e8rsci marteli\u00e9n, ciam\u00e2 \"Il matrimonio di Goldoni\". S\u00e9npre inte qu\u00e9lli \u00e0nni, o l'\u00e0 mostr\u00f2u 'n gr\u00e0nde inter\u00e8sse a-e rif\u00f3rme inandi\u00e6 da-o p\u00e0ppa P\u00eeo IX: l'Aliz\u00earo o l'\u00e0iva def\u00e6ti di f\u00f3rti ide\u00e2li liber\u00e2li, ma 'na s\u00e0lda f\u00eade cat\u00f2lica asc\u00ec. Tra po\u00eaxie e d'\u00f2cax\u00f3n scr\u00eete da l\u00ea, into 1847 l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to stanp\u00f2u a Z\u00eana i \"Fasti di Pio IX raccontati al popolo italiano\"..., con l'out\u00f4 che into m\u00e9ntre o scriv\u00e9iva de l\u00f6de a-o C\u00e0rlo Alb\u00e8rto, o qu\u00e6, pigi\u00e0ndo c\u00f3mme ez\u00e9npio e rif\u00f3rme do p\u00e0ppa, o l'\u00e0iva inandi\u00f2u 'na pol\u00ectica riformatr\u00eexe. Into 1848 o l'\u00e0 colabor\u00f2u con \"Il Pensiero Italiano\", sott'a-a dire\u00e7i\u00f3n de F. Bettini e M. Accame, con do\u00ee art\u00eccoli inti n\u00f9meri 71 e 72, publich\u00e6 rispetivam\u00e9nte a-i 22 e a-i 24 d'arv\u00ee. Into c\u00f3rso da gr\u00e0nde riv\u00f2lta de Z\u00eana do 1849 o l'\u00e0 av\u00fbo 'n r\u00f2llo de mediat\u00f4, scriv\u00e9ndo p\u00f6i, in sce comisci\u00f3n do Com\u00f9n, 'n \"Commentario delle cose accadute in Genova in marzo e in aprile 1849\" inte tr\u00e9i vol\u00f9mmi, ch'o no l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to per\u00f2 public\u00f2u apr\u00eauvo a-o ref\u00fbo de l'out\u00f4 de cangi\u00e2 \u00e7\u00e8rti pas\u00e0ggi.\nDa-o 1850 a-o 1890 o l'\u00e0 insegn\u00f2u, a Z\u00eana, into lic\u00eao Crist\u00f2ffa C\u00f3nbo; into 1846 o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to tra i s\u00f2cci fondato\u00ee da socj\u00eat\u00e6 de st\u00f6ia, gi\u00f6graf\u00eea e archiolog\u00eea, fax\u00e9ndo p\u00e0rte do col\u00eagio di profeso\u00ee da facolt\u00e6 de l\u00e9tie de l'universcit\u00e6. Into 1855 o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to nomin\u00f2u diret\u00f4 do \"Michelangelo\", 'n giorn\u00e2le leter\u00e2io de l'\u00e9poca, pe 'n tot\u00e2le de s\u00e9tte n\u00f9meri. O l'\u00e9 p\u00f6i st\u00e6to prescid\u00e9nte da se\u00e7i\u00f3n de B\u00e9lle \u00c0rte da Socj\u00eat\u00e6 L\u00ecgure d'Ist\u00f6ia P\u00e0tria, da qu\u00e6 o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to un di s\u00f2cci sc\u00ecnn-a da-a s\u00f2 fonda\u00e7i\u00f3n a-i 21 de frev\u00e2 do 1858. Da-o 1866 o l'\u00e0 colabor\u00f2u co-i setiman\u00e2li \"Alba\", test\u00e2 scent\u00ecfico-leter\u00e2ia, a \"Gazzetta di Genova\" e setiman\u00e2le \"Vittorio Alfieri\". Into 1867, l'Aliz\u00earo o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to nomin\u00f2u segret\u00e2io da comisci\u00f3n consult\u00eeva pi-\u00e2 conserva\u00e7i\u00f3n di b\u00eani st\u00f2richi e de b\u00e8lle \u00e0rte e, tr\u00e9i \u00e0nni d\u00f2ppo, o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to incareg\u00f2u de red\u00ecgge 'na l\u00ecsta di cazam\u00e9nti zen\u00e9ixi merit\u00e9voli do t\u00ectolo de \"b\u00eani na\u00e7ion\u00e2li\".\nO l'\u00e0 tegn\u00fbo numer\u00f4ze let\u00fbe de s\u00f2 ri\u00e7\u00e8rche \u00f3ltre che v\u00e0rie confer\u00e9nse in sci\u00e2 Div\u00ecnn-a Com\u00e9dia a-o c\u00ecrcolo filol\u00f2gico m\u00e9ntre o l'\u00eaa der\u00ea a prepar\u00e2 'n'edi\u00e7i\u00f3n do po\u00eama con com\u00e9nto, no go\u00e6i arm\u00f2nica e de v\u00eagio st\u00e0npo, ch'a l'\u00e9 sciort\u00eea a desp\u00e9nse a part\u00ee da-o 1877. O com\u00e9nto o l'\u00eaa form\u00f2u da tr\u00e9i vol\u00f9mmi e o l'\u00eaa preced\u00fbo da 'na l\u00f3nga introdu\u00e7i\u00f3n, inta qu\u00e6 l'Aliz\u00earo o l'\u00e0 rielabor\u00f2u, in sci\u00e2 b\u00e2ze de qu\u00e9lle ci\u00f9 ant\u00eeghe, a biograf\u00eea do po\u00eata, analiz\u00e0ndo e s\u00f2 conce\u00e7io\u00ecn e a p\u00e0rte leter\u00e2ia e filol\u00f2gica da com\u00e9dia. Da-o p\u00f3nto de v\u00ecsta da valuta\u00e7i\u00f3n est\u00e9tica o se ricol\u00eaga a-i pur\u00ecsti, sp\u00e9cce a l'Ant\u00f6nio C\u00e9zari e a-i s\u00e0ggi de Gabri\u00e6lo Ros\u00e9tti, de Vin\u00e7\u00e9nso Giob\u00e9rti e de Niccol\u00f2 Tomaz\u00eao, ariv\u00e0ndo sc\u00ecnn-a-o \"Dante spiegato con Dante\" do Gianbat\u00ecsta Giuli\u00e0n.\nIn sc\u00ee monum\u00e9nti art\u00ecstichi zen\u00e9ixi l'Aliz\u00earo o l'\u00e9 torn\u00f2u con di \u00e2tri scr\u00eeti, public\u00e0ndo, into 1875, a fam\u00f4za \"Guida illustrativa del cittadino e del forestiero per la citt\u00e0 di Genova e sue adiacenze\". A \u00f2gni m\u00f2ddo, a ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte di s\u00f2 st\u00f9ddi a l'\u00e9 dedic\u00e2 a-a ri\u00e7\u00e8rca in sce l'\u00e0rte e i art\u00ecsti l\u00ecguri, public\u00e2 inte d\u00f4e gr\u00e9nde \u00f2pere de \"Notizie dei professori del disegno in Liguria dalla fondazione dell'Accademia\", spart\u00eea inte tr\u00e9i vol\u00f9mmi publich\u00e6 tra o 1864 e o 1866, e de \"Notizie dei professori del disegno in Liguria dalle origini al secolo XVI\", inte s\u00eai vol\u00f9mmi publich\u00e6 tra o 1870 e o 1880. A pr\u00ecmma \u00f2pera, scr\u00eeta con l'id\u00eaa de contino\u00e2 qu\u00e9lle do Sorv\u00e0n e do R\u00e0tto e carateriz\u00e2 da 'na gr\u00e0nde dilig\u00e9nsa docoment\u00e2ia ma limit\u00e2 inte l'inposta\u00e7i\u00f3n e inta pr\u00f6za, a l'\u00e9 a \u00f2gni m\u00f2ddo l'arecug\u00e9ita ci\u00f9 r\u00eccca de informa\u00e7io\u00ecn in sce l'\u00e0rte l\u00ecgure tra a f\u00ecn do s\u00e9colo XVIII e a pr\u00ecmma meit\u00e6 de qu\u00e9llo sucesc\u00eevo. O seg\u00f3ndo scr\u00eeto, co-i pr\u00ecmmi tr\u00e9i vol\u00f9mmi che p\u00e0rlan da pit\u00fba e i \u00e2tri tr\u00e9i dedich\u00e6 a-a scult\u00fba, o preved\u00e9iva in prin\u00e7\u00ecpio tr\u00e9i vol\u00f9mmi in sce l'architet\u00fba asc\u00ec, ma no s\u00f3n st\u00e6ti ci\u00f9 conpil\u00e6. A \u00f2gni m\u00f2ddo, co-i m\u00e6ximi pr\u00eagi e i m\u00e6ximi l\u00ecmiti do r\u00e8sto da s\u00f2 produ\u00e7i\u00f3n, sto t\u00e8sto chi o l'\u00e9 'n'arecug\u00e9ita fondament\u00e2le de docomenta\u00e7i\u00f3n s\u00e9gge in sc\u00ee art\u00ecsti l\u00ecguri sc\u00ecnn-a-o s\u00e9colo XVI che in sce qu\u00e9lli for\u00e8sti ch'\u00e0n travagi\u00f2u in Lig\u00f9ria. Tra i s\u00f2 \u00f9rtimi trav\u00e0ggi se reg\u00f3rda 'na colabora\u00e7i\u00f3n, into 1882, co-o peri\u00f2dico cat\u00f2lico l\"'Elleboro\". A-i 13 d'\u00f2t\u00f4bre do 1882, recovi\u00f2u da-a m\u00f3gge Tex\u00f4 Bol\u00f3n e da-i \u00e7\u00ecnque f\u00ecggi, apr\u00eauvo a 'n c\u00f2rpo l'Aliz\u00earo o l'\u00e9 m\u00f2rto inta s\u00f2 c\u00e2za de canp\u00e0gna a S\u00e0n Gi\u00e2xo, inta val\u00e0dda do Pon\u00e7\u00e9ivia, vegn\u00ecndo in sci\u00e2 f\u00ecn inter\u00f2u into canpos\u00e0nto de Stag\u00e9n.\nA l\u00ea, a \u00e7it\u00e6 de Z\u00eana a l'\u00e0 dedic\u00f2u a str\u00e0dda co-o m\u00e6ximo n\u00f3mme into quart\u00ea de S\u00e0n Teod\u00f6o. In prin\u00e7\u00ecpio ghe n'\u00eaa 'n'\u00e2tra scito\u00e2 a S\u00e0n P\u00ea d'\u00c6nn-a ma, apr\u00eauvo a-a sopresci\u00f3n de qu\u00e9llo com\u00f9n e pe evit\u00e2 di top\u00f2nimi d\u00f3ggi, into 1935 l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to cangi\u00f2u o s\u00f2 n\u00f3mme inte str\u00e0dda de Lo\u00eegi C\u00e0rlo Far\u00e6n."}
{"id": "30104", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=30104", "title": "Open Researcher and Contributor ID", "text": "L'Open Researcher and Contributor ID (in s\u00eegla ORCID, pronon\u00e7i\u00f2u ) o l'\u00e9 'n c\u00f2dice arfanum\u00e9rico no propi\u00eat\u00e2io d\u00eauvi\u00f2u pe identific\u00e2 inte 'n m\u00f2ddo univoco i outo\u00ee e i colaborato\u00ee de comunica\u00e7io\u00ecn acad\u00e9miche, \u00f3ltre a es\u00eeghe 'n sc\u00eeto d'Intern\u00e9tte e di serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i ORCID pe \u00e7erc\u00e2 i outo\u00ee e a s\u00f2 produ\u00e7i\u00f3n bibliogr\u00e0fica, con \u00e2tre informa\u00e7io\u00ecn forn\u00eee da-i ut\u00e9nti. \nInte sto m\u00f2ddo chi se peu ris\u00f2lve o probl\u00eama de contrib\u00fbti de 'n \u00e7\u00e8rto out\u00f4 a-a letiat\u00fba scent\u00ecfica \u00f2 a-e publica\u00e7io\u00ecn che possan \u00ease dif\u00ec\u00e7ili da ricon\u00f3sce, apr\u00eauvo a-o f\u00e6to chi-\u00e2 ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte di n\u00f3mmi no s\u00f3n univochi, p\u00eauan cangi\u00e2 co-o t\u00e9npo, \u00e0n de difer\u00e9nse coltur\u00e2li into s\u00f2 \u00f3rdine e cont\u00eagnan 'n \u00fbzo incoer\u00e9nte de abrevia\u00e7io\u00ecn do n\u00f3mme \u00f2 ad\u00eauvian di scist\u00eami de scrit\u00fba desp\u00e6gi. L'ORCID o forn\u00ecsce 'n'identit\u00e6 perscist\u00e9nte a-e pers\u00f3nn-e, sc\u00ecmile a-o c\u00f2dice fisc\u00e2le, ch'a v\u00ean cre\u00e2 pe-e entit\u00e6 corel\u00e6 a-i contegn\u00fbi in sc\u00ea r\u00e6 digit\u00e2le pe m\u00eazo di indentificato\u00ee di \u00f2g\u00e8tti digit\u00e2li (DOI). \n\u00dbxi.\nL'ORCID o l'am\u00eea de forn\u00ee 'n c\u00f2dice perscist\u00e9nte a-e pers\u00f3nn-e, de m\u00f2ddo da ris\u00f2lve o probl\u00eama che i contrib\u00fbti de 'n \u00e7\u00e8rto out\u00f4 a-a comunica\u00e7i\u00f3n scent\u00ecfica possan \u00ease dif\u00ec\u00e7ili da ricon\u00f3sce, zach\u00e9 a ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte di n\u00f3mmi person\u00e2li a no l'\u00e9 univoca e d\u00f3nca ci\u00f9 sog\u00e9tti co-o m\u00e6ximo n\u00f3mme pori\u00e9ivan contribo\u00ee into m\u00e6ximo c\u00e0npo scent\u00ecfico \u00f2 adreit\u00fba into m\u00e6ximo dipartim\u00e9nto institu\u00e7ion\u00e2le. Pe de ci\u00f9, i n\u00f3mmi p\u00eauan cangi\u00e2 (prez\u00e9npio co-o mai\u00e9zzo); gh'\u00e9 p\u00f6i de difer\u00e9nse coltur\u00e2li inte l'\u00f3rdine di n\u00f3mmi; e rev\u00ecste f\u00e0n 'n \u00fbzo incoer\u00e9nte de abrevia\u00e7io\u00ecn do n\u00f3mme, di s\u00f2 suf\u00ecsci e de ini\u00e7i\u00e2le do seg\u00f3ndo n\u00f3mme; e ad\u00eauvian di scist\u00eami de scrit\u00fba difer\u00e9nti.\nL'\u00f2rganiza\u00e7i\u00f3n ch'a gest\u00ecsce l'ORCID, l'ORCID Inc., a forn\u00ecsce a t\u00f9tti i ut\u00e9nti registr\u00e6 a poscibilit\u00e6 de mantegn\u00ee 'n \u00f9nico \"curriculum vitae\" digit\u00e2le agiorn\u00f2u in continoa\u00e7i\u00f3n e ch'o forn\u00ecsce 'n qu\u00e0ddro di s\u00f2 contrib\u00fbti a-a sc\u00e9nsa ch'o va a-o de la da s\u00e9nplice l\u00ecsta de publica\u00e7io\u00ecn, \u00f2spit\u00f2u da l'ORCID e cur\u00f2u da l'ut\u00e9nte.\nSt\u00f6ia.\nSvil\u00f9ppo e sl\u00e0nso.\nL'ORCID o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to anon\u00e7i\u00f2u pi-\u00e2 pr\u00ecmma v\u00f2tta into 2009 c\u00f3mme 'n sf\u00f2rso colaborat\u00eevo da p\u00e0rte di edito\u00ee de ri\u00e7\u00e8rche acad\u00e9miche \"pe ris\u00f2lve o probl\u00eama de l'anbigoit\u00e6 do n\u00f3mme de l'out\u00f4 inta comunica\u00e7i\u00f3n acad\u00e9mica\". A \"Open Researcher Contributor Identification Initiative\", d\u00f3nd'o v\u00ean o n\u00f3mme ORCID, a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta cre\u00e2 in v\u00eea tenpor\u00e0nia pr\u00ecmma de l'incorpora\u00e7i\u00f3n.\n'N prot\u00f2tipo o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to svilup\u00f2u in sce 'n software adat\u00f2u da qu\u00e9llo d\u00eauvi\u00f2u da-o Thomson Reuters p\u00f2-u s\u00f2 scist\u00eama ResearcherID. L'ORCID Inc. a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta costito\u00eea c\u00f3mme 'n'\u00f2rganiza\u00e7i\u00f3n indipend\u00e9nte s\u00e9nsa f\u00ecn de go\u00e2gno inte l'ag\u00f3sto do 2010, baz\u00e2 into st\u00e2to americ\u00e0n do Delaware e co-in cons\u00e8ggio d'aministra\u00e7i\u00f3n interna\u00e7ion\u00e2le. O s\u00f2 diret\u00f4 esecut\u00eevo, o Chris Shillum, o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to nomin\u00f2u into set\u00e9nbre do 2020, suced\u00e9ndo a-o fondat\u00f4 de l'\u00f2rganiza\u00e7i\u00f3n, o Laurel Haak, nomin\u00f2u inte l'arv\u00ee do 2012. Da-o 2016 o cons\u00e8ggio d'aministra\u00e7i\u00f3n o l'\u00e9 prescjed\u00fbo da Veronique Kiermer, de PLOS (qu\u00e9llo de pr\u00ecmma o l'\u00eaa Ed Pentz, de Crossref). ORCID o peu \u00ease d\u00eauvi\u00f2u liberam\u00e9nte e ins\u00e9mme a \u00e2tri scist\u00eami de identifica\u00e7i\u00f3n. A-i 16 d'\u00f2t\u00f4bre do 2012, l'ORCID Inc. a l'\u00e0 avi\u00f2u i s\u00f2 serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i de reg\u00ecstro e a l'\u00e0 comens\u00f2u a relasci\u00e2 i identificato\u00ee a-i ut\u00e9nti.\nAdo\u00e7i\u00f3n.\nPe incorag\u00ee \u00e2tri ut\u00e9nti a un\u00eese a l'ORCID de m\u00f2ddo da sostegn\u00eene l'ado\u00e7i\u00f3n, a-o pr\u00ecmmo de zen\u00e2 do 2016 l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to scr\u00eeto 'na l\u00e9tia av\u00e8rta inta qu\u00e6 v\u00ean aferm\u00f2u che \"i edito\u00ee ch'\u00e0n firm\u00f2u sta l\u00e9tia av\u00e8rta chi se s\u00f3n inpegn\u00e6 a domand\u00e2 i iD ORCID an\u00e0ndo apr\u00eauvo a-i st\u00e0ndard de inplementa\u00e7i\u00f3n spec\u00ecfichi\".\nInte 'n agiornam\u00e9nto do 2021 in sci\u00f4 sc\u00eeto d'Intern\u00e9tte de Springer Nature, l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to diciar\u00f2u che da qu\u00e9llo mom\u00e9nto \"a sai\u00e2 suport\u00e2 a ver\u00ecfica e l'acr\u00e9dito da v\u00f2stra ativit\u00e6 \"peer reviewed\" diretam\u00e9nte da-i n\u00f2stri scist\u00eami de spedi\u00e7i\u00f3n di manoscr\u00eeti a ORCID\".\nIdentificato\u00ee.\nFormalm\u00e9nte, i ID ORCID s\u00f3n specifich\u00e6 c\u00f3mme di URI; prez\u00e9npio qu\u00e9llo do Josiah S. Carberry, 'n profes\u00f4 de fantax\u00eea de sp\u00e9sso d\u00eauvi\u00f2u inti ez\u00e9npi, o l'\u00e9 https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1825-0097, co-i form\u00e2ti https:// e http:// che s\u00f3n suport\u00e6 t\u00f9tti do\u00ee, scib\u00e9n ch\u00f2-u pr\u00ecmmo o l'\u00e9 divent\u00f2u a r\u00e9gola a part\u00ee da-o nov\u00e9nbre do 2017. A \u00f2gni m\u00f2ddo, gh'\u00e9 di edito\u00ee che l'ad\u00eauvian inte 'na f\u00f3rma ci\u00f9 br\u00eave, prez\u00e9npio ORCID: 0000-0002-1825-0097, c\u00f3mme s'o fo\u00eese 'n URN.\nI ID ORCID s\u00f3n 'n sotoins\u00e9mme de l'International Standard Name Identifier (ISNI), seg\u00f3ndo i oug\u00f9ri de l'\u00d2rganiza\u00e7i\u00f3n Interna\u00e7ion\u00e2le pi-\u00e2 Standardiza\u00e7i\u00f3n (c\u00f3mme ISO 27729), co-e d\u00f4e \u00f2rganiza\u00e7io\u00ecn che st\u00e0n colabor\u00e0ndo ativam\u00e9nte. L'ISNI o fai\u00e2 'n identifica\u00e7i\u00f3n univoca di colaborato\u00ee di l\u00ecbbri, progr\u00e0mmi televix\u00eevi e giorn\u00e2li e o l'\u00e0 riserv\u00f2u 'n bl\u00f2cco de identificato\u00ee pe l'\u00fbzo da p\u00e0rte de l'ORCID inte l'interv\u00e0llo da 0000-0001-5000-0007 a 0000-0003-5000-0001. L'\u00e9 d\u00f3nca posc\u00ecbile che 'na pers\u00f3nn-a a l'\u00e0gge s\u00e9gge 'n ISBN che 'n ID ORCID e d\u00f3nca, inta pr\u00e0tica, do\u00ee ISBN.\nS\u00e9gge l'ORCID che l'ISNI ad\u00eauvian di identificato\u00ee a 16 car\u00e0teri, con c\u00eefre da 0 a 9 separ\u00e6 inte gr\u00f9ppi de qu\u00e0ttro da di trat\u00ecn. O car\u00e0tere fin\u00e2le o peu \u00ease 'na l\u00e9tia \"X\" asc\u00ec, ch'a raprez\u00e9nta 'n val\u00f4 de 10 (prez\u00e9npio l'ID ORCID de Stephen Hawking o l'\u00e9 0000-0002-9079-593X), e o l'\u00e9 'na c\u00eefra de contr\u00f2llo MOD 11-2 in conformit\u00e6 co-o st\u00e0ndard ISO/IEC 7064:2003.\nM\u00e9nbri, sp\u00f2nsor e registr\u00e0nti.\nA-a f\u00ecn do 2013, l'ORCID a cont\u00e2va de 111 \u00f2rganiza\u00e7io\u00ecn asoci\u00e6 e ci\u00f9 de 460.000 registr\u00e0nti. A-i 15 de nov\u00e9nbre do 2014, l'ORCID a l'anon\u00e7i\u00f2u a s\u00f2 milion\u00eaxima registra\u00e7i\u00f3n e, a-i 20 de nov\u00e9nbre do 2020, a l'\u00e0 super\u00f2u i pr\u00ecmmi d\u00eaxe milio\u00ecn. Tra i m\u00e9nbri de l'\u00f2rganiza\u00e7i\u00f3n gh'\u00e9 v\u00e0rri instit\u00fbti de ri\u00e7\u00e8rca, c\u00f3mme Caltech e a Cornell University, e edito\u00ee c\u00f3mme Elsevier, Springer, Wiley e Nature Publishing Group. Gh'\u00e9 asc\u00ec de inpr\u00e9ize comerci\u00e2li, c\u00f3mme Thomson Reuters, socj\u00eat\u00e6 acad\u00e9miche e \u00e9nti de finan\u00e7iam\u00e9nto.\n\u00c0nche i \u00e9nti che d\u00e0n de soven\u00e7io\u00ecn, c\u00f3mme a Wellcome Trust, 'na fonda\u00e7i\u00f3n de benefic\u00e9nsa, \u00e0n comens\u00f2u a inp\u00f3nn-e a qu\u00e9lli che dom\u00e0ndan 'n finan\u00e7iam\u00e9nto de forn\u00ee 'n identificat\u00f4 ORCID.\nInplementa\u00e7io\u00ecn na\u00e7ion\u00e2li.\nInte v\u00e0rri st\u00e2ti gh'\u00e9 di cons\u00f2r\u00e7\u00e7i, che incl\u00f9ddan di \u00e9nti governat\u00eevi c\u00f3mme p\u00e0rtner, che st\u00e0n travagi\u00e0ndo a liv\u00e9llo na\u00e7ion\u00e2le pe inplement\u00e2 l'ORCID. Prez\u00e9npio inte l'It\u00e0lia gh'\u00e9 set\u00e0nta universcit\u00e6 e qu\u00e0ttro c\u00e9ntri de ri\u00e7\u00e8rca in colabora\u00e7i\u00f3n sott'a-a confer\u00e9nsa di reto\u00ee de universcit\u00e6 itali\u00e0nn-e (CRUI) e de l'agen\u00e7\u00eea na\u00e7ion\u00e2le de valuta\u00e7i\u00f3n de l'universcit\u00e6 e di instit\u00fbti de ri\u00e7\u00e8rca (ANVUR), inte l'\u00e0nbito de 'n prog\u00e8tto inandi\u00f2u da-o Cineca, 'n cons\u00f2r\u00e7io no-profit ch'o raprez\u00e9nta e universcit\u00e6, i instit\u00fbti de ri\u00e7\u00e8rca e o minist\u00earo de l'instru\u00e7i\u00f3n. Inte l'Oustr\u00e0lia, o National Health and Medical Research Council (NHMRC) e l'Australian Research Council (ARC) \"incor\u00e0gian t\u00f9tti i ri\u00e7ercato\u00ee che dom\u00e0ndan 'n finan\u00e7iam\u00e9nto a av\u00e9i 'n indentificat\u00f4 ORCID\". L'HAL, 'n arch\u00ecvio fran\u00e7\u00e9ize de art\u00eccoli scent\u00ecfichi, o dom\u00e0nda a-i s\u00f2 ut\u00e9nti de inser\u00ee o pr\u00f2pio identificat\u00eevo ORCID.\nIntegra\u00e7io\u00ecn.\nS\u00e9gge Wikipedia che Wikidata incl\u00f9ddan p\u00e0gine con identificato\u00ee ORCID.\nA part\u00ee da-o 2014, \u00f3ltre a-i m\u00e9nbri e a-i sp\u00f2nsor, rev\u00ecste, edito\u00ee e \u00e2tri serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i \u00e0n incl\u00fbzo \u00f2 \u00e0ivan za incl\u00fbzo l'ORCID inti s\u00f2 fl\u00f9sci de trav\u00e0ggio \u00f2 b\u00e0nche d\u00e6ti. Tra o 2014 e o 2016 di serv\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i in sci\u00e2 R\u00e6 \u00e0n cre\u00f2u di strum\u00e9nti pe esport\u00e2 i d\u00e6ti v\u00e8rso, \u00f2p\u00fb inport\u00e2li da, l'ORCID.\nInte l'\u00f2t\u00f4bre do 2015, DataCite, Crossref e ORCID \u00e0n anon\u00e7i\u00f2u che-e pr\u00ecmme \u00f2rganiza\u00e7io\u00ecn avi\u00e9ivan agiorn\u00f2u i elem\u00e9nti ORCID \"qu\u00e0nde 'n identificat\u00f4 ORCID o vegn\u00ecsse trov\u00f2u inte n\u00f3mmi DOI ap\u00e9nn-a registr\u00e6\".\n\u00c7\u00e8rti d\u00e6ti ORCID p\u00eauan \u00ease ricuper\u00e6 c\u00f3mme RDF/XML, RDF Turtle, XML \u00f2 JSON asc\u00ec. L'ORCID o l'ad\u00eauvia GitHub c\u00f3mme s\u00f2 arch\u00ecvio de c\u00f2dichi."}
