{"id": "30167", "revid": "1211", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=30167", "title": "Pontevedra", "text": "Pontevedra (in gali\u00e7i\u00e0n pronon\u00e7i\u00f2u , in castili\u00e0n ) o l'\u00e9 'n com\u00fbne spagn\u00f2llo de 83.260 abit\u00e0nti, capol\u00eaugo de l'\u00f2m\u00f2nima prov\u00ecnsa, ch'o se tr\u00eauva inta comunit\u00e6 out\u00f2noma da Gal\u00ec\u00e7ia. A s\u00f2 \u00e0rea metropolit\u00e0nn-a a cont\u00e2va, a-o 2008, 149.255 abit\u00e0nti.\nComunica\u00e7io\u00ecn.\nStr\u00e0dde.\nA \u00e7it\u00e6 de Pontevedra a l'\u00e9 serv\u00eea da-e outostr\u00e0dde elench\u00e6 chi de s\u00f3tta:\nFerov\u00eee e trasp\u00f2rti p\u00f9blichi.\nPontevedra a l'\u00e9 coleg\u00e2 a-a r\u00e6 ferovi\u00e0ria a \u00e2ta velocit\u00e6 spagn\u00f2lla (AVE), atrav\u00e8rso a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Pontevedra, con colegam\u00e9nti co-o r\u00e8sto da Gal\u00ec\u00e7ia e da na\u00e7i\u00f3n asc\u00ec.\nO trasp\u00f2rto p\u00f9blico o l'\u00e9 garant\u00eeo da v\u00e0rie l\u00ecnie de cori\u00eare urb\u00e2ne e numer\u00f4ze l\u00ecnie \u00e8stra-urb\u00e2ne, \u00f3ltre che 'na fl\u00f2tta de tasc\u00ec."}
