{"id": "30178", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=30178", "title": "Les\u00e0ndria", "text": ""}
{"id": "30179", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=30179", "title": "P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n", "text": "O P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n (\"Pa\u00eds Valenci\u00e0\" in catal\u00e0n, \"Pa\u00eds Valenciano\" in spagn\u00f2llo) o l'\u00e9 'n p\u00e0ize de l'Eur\u00f2pa e do Mediterr\u00e0neo scito\u00f2u a-o levante da pen\u00eezoa Ib\u00e8rica. Co-a denomina\u00e7i\u00f3n ofi\u00e7i\u00e2 de Comunit\u00e6 Valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a (\"Comunitat Valenciana\", in catal\u00e0n e ofi\u00e7ialm\u00e9nte), into 1982 o se constitu\u00ecsce c\u00f3mme 'na com\u00fbnit\u00e6 out\u00f2noma da Spagna, d\u00f2ppo d'av\u00e9i aced\u00fbo a l'aotogov\u00e6rno into 1978 co-o Cons\u00e9ggio do P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n, precors\u00f4 de l'ato\u00e2le Cons\u00e9ggio da Generalit\u00e6 Valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a. D'ac\u00f2rdio co-o seu Stat\u00fbto d'Outonom\u00eea, i seu abit\u00e0nti, o p\u00f2polo valen\u00e7i\u00e0n, s\u00f3n conscider\u00e6 'na na\u00e7ionalit\u00e6 st\u00f2rica. A seu \u00f2r\u00ecgine st\u00f2rica a remonta a-o Regno de Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia, entit\u00e6 politica, leg\u00e2le e aministrat\u00eeva fond\u00e2 into 1239, e con validit\u00e6 fin a-o 1707.\nGeograficam\u00e9nte, o s'est\u00e9nde da-o sci\u00f9mme S\u00e9nia f\u00ecn a Pil\u00e0r de la Forad\u00e0da, ci\u00f9 in l\u00e0 da f\u00f4xe do sci\u00f9mme Seg\u00f3ra, con 'na front\u00eaa ter\u00e8stre de 834\u00a0km de longhixe, e 644\u00a0km de c\u00f2sta. \u00c0nche e izoe mediter\u00e0nee de N\u00eauva Tab\u00f2rca e e Colombr\u00e9te, cosc\u00ec c\u00f3mme \u00e2tre izoe mino\u00ee vex\u00ecnn-e, son d'aministra\u00e7i\u00f3n valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a; o s'est\u00e9nde asc\u00ec pe-o Cant\u00f3n d'Adem\u00f9s, in terit\u00f6io valen\u00e7i\u00e0n contorn\u00f2u da-o com\u00f9n aragon\u00e9ize e conch\u00e9ize.\nA seu \u00f2r\u00ecgine a remonta a-o s\u00e9colo\u00a0XIII, co-a coloniza\u00e7i\u00f3n feod\u00e2le di catal\u00e9n e di aragon\u00e9ixi, fondamentalm\u00e9nte e pe qu\u00e9sto \u00f3rdine, di regni de taifi isl\u00e0michi de Balans\u00ecya, Alp\u00f2nt, D\u00e0niyya, e parte da M\u00f9r\u00e7ia. Unn-a v\u00f2tta fin\u00eea qu\u00e9sta conqu\u00ecsta, o r\u00e8 Gi\u00e0como I o prom\u00f9lga i Furs de Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia into 1261 inandi\u00e0ndo o Regno de Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia, con drito teritori\u00e2le privat\u00eevo inte ci\u00f9 de qu\u00e0tro s\u00e9coli. L'indipend\u00e9nsa leg\u00e2le do regno a ven abol\u00eea into 1707 co-i Decreti de N\u00eauva Ci\u00e0nta em\u00ecssi da-o r\u00e8 F\u00e9ipo V de Cast\u00ecgla, conosci\u00fbo c\u00f3mme \"Felip\" \"el Socarrat\" asc\u00ec. E pr\u00ecmme pr\u00eauve pe recovi\u00e2 l'aotogov\u00e6rno int'a f\u00ecn do secolo\u00a0XIX e o prin\u00e7\u00ecpio do XX son st\u00e6te del\u00f9ze pe-e ditat\u00fbe de quelli mom\u00e9nti. Inti \u00e0nni 60 do s\u00e9colo XX, a dom\u00e0nda d'aotogov\u00e6rno da desp\u00e6gie corr\u00e9nti ideol\u00f2giche a l'\u00e9 rezurt\u00e2 inta constitu\u00e7i\u00f3n do Cons\u00e9ggio do P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n in 1978. Finalm\u00e9nte, into 1982, l'aotogov\u00e6rno o s'apr\u00eauva formalm\u00e9nte co-in Stat\u00fbto d'Aotonom\u00eea ch'o l'\u00e0 st\u00e6to reform\u00f2u into 2006.\nAministrativam\u00e9nte, o lim\u00ecta a pon\u00e9nte con Cast\u00ecgla-la M\u00e0ncia e l'Arag\u00f3nn-a, a-o sud con M\u00f9r\u00e7ia, e a-o n\u00f6rd con Catal\u00f3gna. Con 5.051.250 abit\u00e0nti (\u00e0nno 2021), o reprez\u00e9nta 'n 35,6% da popola\u00e7i\u00f3n tot\u00e2le di terit\u00f6i de p\u00e0rla catal\u00e0nn-a scib\u00e9n ch'a gh\u00ecfra d'abit\u00e0nti a l'\u00e9 t\u00e0nto supei\u00f4 se son cont\u00e6 i abit\u00e0nti co-a seg\u00f3nda c\u00e2za d'\u00e2tri p\u00e0ixi d'Eur\u00f2pa e di inmigr\u00f2i no cens\u00eeti. Cosc\u00ec, le \u00e7it\u00e6 ci\u00f9 gr\u00e0nde de 100.000 abit\u00e0nti son: Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia (800.180 abit\u00e0nti in 2021), Alac\u00e0nt (337.482 abit\u00e0nti in 2020), \u00c8lx (234.765 abit\u00e0nti in 2020) i Castegl\u00f3 de la Pl\u00e0na (174.264 abit\u00e0nti in 2020).\nSt\u00f6ia.\nEt\u00e6 ant\u00eega.\nDa-a preist\u00f6ia gh'\u00e9 a registra\u00e7i\u00f3n da pr\u00ecmma prez\u00e9nsa um\u00e0nn-a a-e t\u00e6re valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-e pr\u00f2scima do s\u00e9colo XI aC, con descov\u00e6rte di neandert\u00e2li a-a Gr\u00f2tta Neigra (Sci\u00e0tiva), e gr\u00f2tte do Salt (Alc\u00f2i) e do Coc\u00ecno (Vigl\u00e9na). Da l'et\u00e6 cl\u00e0scica o P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n o se ritegn\u00ee c\u00f3mme 'na p\u00e0rte ci\u00f9 import\u00e0nte da civiliza\u00e7i\u00f3n \u00ecbera. Qu\u00e9sto p\u00f2polo (\u00f2, ci\u00f9 b\u00e9n, p\u00f2poli) o l'\u00e0 o seu \u00f2r\u00ecgine inti popola\u00e7io\u00ecn ind\u00ecgene de l'et\u00e6 do br\u00f3nzo che mantegn\u00ecvan di int\u00e9nsi sc\u00e0ngi commer\u00e7i\u00e6 e coltur\u00e6 con tart\u00e9izi, gr\u00eaghi e fen\u00eeci, e qu\u00e9llo o culminari\u00e6 co-o seu splend\u00f4 pr\u00f2scimo do s\u00e9colo V aC, c\u00f3mme o refl\u00e8te a seu produ\u00e7i\u00f3n art\u00ecstica, a ci\u00f9 import\u00e0nte espresci\u00f3n da qu\u00e6 a l'\u00e9 a D\u00e0mma d'\u00c8lx.\nE gu\u00e6re tra cartagin\u00e9izi e rom\u00e9n, result\u00e2to de-e qu\u00e6 o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to a sotomisci\u00f3n de t\u00f9tta a c\u00f2sta valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a a l'aotorit\u00e6 de R\u00f3mma a-o prin\u00e7\u00ecpio do s\u00e9colo III aC, no lev\u00f3n da m\u00eazo a colt\u00fba ib\u00e8rica, perch\u00e9 anc\u00f3n gh'attrov\u00e9mmo import\u00e0nti manifesta\u00e7io\u00ecn art\u00ecstiche do p\u00f2sto, c\u00f3mme e t\u00e6re r\u00f3sse pitu\u00e6 con mot\u00eevi figuat\u00eevi \u00f2 narat\u00eevi, f\u00ecn a-o s\u00e9colo pr\u00ecmmo. L'acoltua\u00e7i\u00f3n, cosc\u00ec, a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta progres\u00eeva. L'\u00f2r\u00ecgine da vertebra\u00e7i\u00f3n do P\u00e0ize Valenci\u00e0n o l'appaisce int'a romaniza\u00e7i\u00f3n, in g\u00eeo da fonda\u00e7i\u00f3n da col\u00f2nia Valentia Edetanorum (Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia) l'\u00e0nno 158 aC e da col\u00f2nia Julia Illici Augusta (\u00c8lx) a-o s\u00e9colo I aC, pe de ci\u00f9 e divixo\u00ecn da prov\u00ecnsa Ilercav\u00f2nia a-o n\u00f6rd, Edet\u00e0nia a-o \u00e7\u00e9ntro e Contest\u00e0nia tra o Sci\u00f3cher e o Seg\u00f3ra, seg\u00f3ndo a pr\u00ecmma prez\u00e9nsa di p\u00f2poli ib\u00e8richi.\nEt\u00e6 de m\u00eazo.\nDap\u00eau da sfregoggia\u00e7i\u00f3n de l'Imp\u00eaio Rom\u00e0n, da-o prin\u00e7\u00ecpio do s\u00e9colo VII f\u00ecnn-a l'in\u00e0ndiu do VIII, gr\u00e0nde p\u00e0rte do terit\u00f6io a l'\u00eaa sog\u00e8to a-o regno visig\u00f4 de Tol\u00e9do, e l'\u00e2tra p\u00e0rte a l'\u00eaa scignoez\u00e2 pr\u00ecmma da l'Imp\u00eaio Rom\u00e0n de Lev\u00e0nte e, d\u00f2ppo, da-o regno de Tudmir, con capol\u00eaugo a Ori\u00f2la. O p\u00e0tto d'Abd al-Aziz con Tudmir l'\u00e0nno 713 o l'\u00e0iva permisso l'intr\u00e2 di \u00e0rabi into terit\u00f6io, co-a qu\u00e6 a com\u00e9nsa unn-a de-e fase ci\u00f9 import\u00e0nte do P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n: Al-\u00c0ndalos. Con t\u00f9tto che qu\u00e9sta \u00e9poca anc\u00f3n a no l'\u00e9 abb\u00e0sta studi\u00e2, e a l'\u00e9 un di peri\u00f3di ci\u00f9 sc\u00f9o da seu st\u00f6ia, l'import\u00e0nsa de l'influ\u00e9nsa da seu colt\u00fba e l\u00e9ngoa in sci\u00e2 colt\u00fba valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a mod\u00e6rna a l'\u00e9 generalm\u00e9nte a\u00e7ett\u00e2, e a fava de Xarq al-\u00c0ndalos un di l\u00eaughi ci\u00f9 c\u00f9lti d'Eur\u00f3pa.\n\u00c0 \u00f2gni m\u00f2ddo, l'\u00f2rigine dir\u00e8tto e ci\u00f9 lont\u00e0n do P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n mod\u00e6rno o s'attr\u00eauva prin\u00e7ip\u00e0lmente lig\u00f2u a-a fonda\u00e7i\u00f3n do Regno de Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia, de nat\u00fba feod\u00e2le: inte l'\u00e0nno 1233 o r\u00e8 Gi\u00e0como o Conquistad\u00f4 o com\u00e9nsa a conquist\u00e2 di terit\u00f6i segn\u00e6 pe trei s\u00e9coli da prez\u00e9nsa sara\u00ecnn-a: i regni de taifi de Balans\u00ecya, D\u00e0niyya e M\u00f9r\u00e7ia. T\u00f9tto gi\u00f9sto fond\u00f2u o regno, sci b\u00e9n ch'a gh'arest\u00e0va a popola\u00e7i\u00f3n tagar\u00ecnn-a sorviat\u00f9tto, se ghe favan de repopola\u00e7io\u00ecn di col\u00f2ni cresti\u00e9n d'\u00f2r\u00ecgine catal\u00e9n e aragon\u00e9ize prin\u00e7ipalm\u00e9nte. Qu\u00e9sti cresti\u00e9n ristrutu\u00f3n l'econom\u00eea e \u00f2rganizz\u00f3n o terit\u00f6io in gio pe-e \u00e7it\u00e6 con derepresenta\u00e7io\u00ecn inte l'asenbl\u00eaa legistat\u00eeva valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a. Inte l'\u00e0nno 1304 o regno o s'estend\u00eava f\u00ecnn-a Ori\u00f2la pe-a sent\u00e9nsa de Torr\u00e9gles, e z\u00e0 o l'\u00eaa prov\u00ecsto de 'na condi\u00e7i\u00f3n politicam\u00e9nte independ\u00e9nte co-i Furs de Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia da l'\u00e0nno 1262, mentre a so\u00e7iet\u00e6 valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a a svilup\u00e2va a seu identit\u00e6 privat\u00eeva, asc\u00ec b\u00e9n che a scompart\u00ecva r\u00e8, colt\u00fba e l\u00e9ngoa co-i terit\u00f6i isp\u00e0nichi da Cor\u00f3nn-a d'Arag\u00f3nn-a.\nEt\u00e6 mod\u00e6rna.\nTre 1519 e 1521, i corpora\u00e7io\u00ecn arm\u00e6, con l'ale\u00e0nsa da borghex\u00eea e di paiz\u00e9n cresti\u00e9n, lot\u00f3n c\u00f3ntra a nobilit\u00e6 e l'aristrocra\u00e7\u00eea (soll\u00eavo de les German\u00eces). Mas se gh'impon\u00e9n i n\u00f2bili, agiut\u00e6 pe-i seu s\u00e8rvi mod\u00e8giari e l'aristocrac\u00eea castegl\u00e0nn-a. Al\u00f4a, a vicer\u00e8nn-a, Germana de Foix, a l'aprofit\u00f2 pe pratic\u00e2 'na f\u00f2rte represci\u00f3n; sto o l'\u00e9 o mom\u00e8nto che com\u00e9nsa a casteglanisa\u00e7i\u00f3n da nobilit\u00e6. \u00c0nche o comens\u00f2 o \"probl\u00eama mor\u00ecsco\" quande l'autorit\u00e6 religi\u00f4za a l'atrov\u00f2 varsci\u00fbi i bat\u00e9zi costr\u00e9iti ch'i paiz\u00e9n av\u00e9ivan apprich\u00e6 a-i mod\u00e8giari, de main\u00ea che vegn\u00ecn n\u00eauvi cresti\u00e9n (1525). L'\u00e0nno 1563, F\u00e9ipo II o command\u00e0va o disarmam\u00e9nto di mor\u00ecschi valen\u00e7i\u00e9n prevegn\u00ecndo posc\u00ecbili soll\u00eavi, pe cax\u00f3n da import\u00e0nsa de qu\u00e9sto gr\u00f9ppo ino Regno de Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia.\nCo-i vicer\u00e8, ar\u00e7iv\u00e9scovo e capit\u00e0gno gener\u00e2le Joan de Ribera, a cor\u00f3nn-a a l'atrov\u00f2 'n instrum\u00e9nto m\u00e2vegi\u00f4zo pe pratic\u00e2 o central\u00ecsmo e le dotr\u00ecnn-e da Contraref\u00f3rma. In 1609, F\u00e9ipo III (1598-1621) o decret\u00f2 l'espulsci\u00f3n de 135.000 morischi. A p\u00e6dia t\u00f9tt'as\u00e9mme de 'n t\u00e6rso da popola\u00e7ion a supon\u00e9iva 'n gr\u00e9ive d\u00e0nno econ\u00f2mico, particolam\u00e9nte ino c\u00e0mpo perch\u00e9 o l'\u00eaa d\u00f3nde i morischi travagi\u00e0van. \u00c0 \u00f2gni m\u00f2ddo, Manuel Ardit o f\u00e0va v\u00e9dde che l'espulsci\u00f3n o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta 'n st\u00ecmolo pe l'arso\u00eeocolt\u00fba e le consegu\u00e9nse demogr\u00e0fiche torn\u00f3n a-a normalit\u00e6 v\u00e6rso a f\u00ecnn-a de s\u00e9colo XVII. \nQuante \u00e0-a colt\u00fba e l'\u00e2rte, a prin\u00e7\u00ecpio de l'et\u00e6 mod\u00e6rna res\u00e2t\u00f3n o fil\u00f2sofo Joan Llu\u00eds Vives e o pitt\u00f4 Joan de Joanes. Do peri\u00f3do apr\u00eauvo devan \u00ease nomin\u00f2u i pitto\u00ee Francesc Ribalta e Josep de Ribera, i scorto\u00ee Ignasi i Josep Vergara e o muxic\u00ecsta Joan Baptista Cabaniles.\nDap\u00eau da n\u00f2mina econ\u00f2mica, so\u00e7i\u00e2le e colt\u00fbal do s\u00e9colo d'\u00f6o propi\u00e7i\u00e2 pe l'espansci\u00f3n mediterr\u00e0nea da cor\u00f3nn-a d'Arag\u00f3nn-a a-o s\u00e9colo XV, e dov\u00fbo a-i confl\u00ectti so\u00e7i\u00e2li, a Gu\u00e6ra de Sucesci\u00f3n spagn\u00f2lla e i Decreti de N\u00eauva Ci\u00e0nta (1707) sfreg\u00f3ggian o regno co-a deroga\u00e7i\u00f3n di Furs; o p\u00e0ize o pass\u00f2 \u00e0 form\u00e2 p\u00e0rte do Regno de Spagna.\nEt\u00e6 contempor\u00e0nga e prez\u00e9nte.\nInte o s\u00e9colo XIX, o P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n o m\u00f3nta le \u00e2ie cortiv\u00e6, sorviat\u00f9tto qu\u00e9lle rela\u00e7ion\u00e6 co-a coltiva\u00e7i\u00f3n d'\u00fbga, r\u00eeso, \u00e7etro\u00ecn e am\u00e0ndoa. O c\u00e0ngio v\u00e9rso l'ind\u00f9stria o peu ino qu\u00e2rto l\u00eaugo do st\u00e0to spang\u00f2llo f\u00ecnn-a \u00f2ua. A prin\u00e7\u00ecpio do s\u00e9colo XX, a societ\u00e6 valenci\u00e0nn-a a recl\u00e0ma l'aotogov\u00e6rno do seu p\u00e0ize e, dap\u00eau de 'na pr\u00ecmma pr\u00eauva \u00e0-a Seg\u00f3nda Rep\u00f9brica Spagn\u00f2lla e an\u00e6to apr\u00eauvo de 'n per\u00ecodo de totalitar\u00ecsmo, finalm\u00e9nte o disp\u00f3ne d'outonom\u00eea in 1977 inta Tranxi\u00e7i\u00f3n Spagn\u00f2lla. Inta seg\u00f3nda meit\u00e6 de qu\u00e9sto s\u00e9colo, un n\u00eauvo sett\u00f4 econ\u00f2mico che praticam\u00e9nte o sostit\u00f4e l'agricolt\u00fba a liv\u00e9llo de gu\u00e2gni econ\u00f2michi: o tur\u00ecsmo. Con l'aprova\u00e7i\u00f3n do Stat\u00f3to in 1982, o l'arec\u00f3via o seu gov\u00e6rno pr\u00f2pio, a Generalit\u00e6 Valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a, 15 che a ne aseg\u00f9a l'amisitra\u00e7i\u00f3n.\nA-o s\u00e9colo XXI, o gh'\u00e0 apparso 'n pensc\u00eao sci\u00f9 a discrimina\u00e7i\u00f3n finansi\u00e2ia vers'a Comunit\u00e6 Valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a pe-o Stato Spagnol. O m\u00e0zo de 2016, o Tribun\u00e2 Constitu\u00e7ion\u00e2le o scas\u00f2 a L\u00e9ze 10/2007 de reg\u00ecme matrimoni\u00e2le valenci\u00e0n, che a l'abilit\u00e0va 'n c\u00f2dixe \u00e7iv\u00eele pr\u00f2pio, perm\u00ecsso pe-o Stat\u00f3to d'Outonom\u00eea.\nL\u00e9ngoe.\nO valen\u00e7i\u00e0n, n\u00f3mme ch'o re\u00e7\u00e9ive a l\u00e9ngoa catal\u00e0nn-a into P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n, M\u00f9r\u00e7ia e p\u00e0rte da regi\u00f3n aragon\u00e9ize do Matarr\u00e0gna, o l'\u00e9 reconosci\u00fbo c\u00f3mme l\u00e9ngoa pr\u00f2pia da Generalit\u00e6 co-a L\u00eaze d'\u00dbzo e Insegnam\u00e9nto do 1983, e do p\u00e0ize in gener\u00e2le da 2006 pe-o Stat\u00fbto. A-o mom\u00e9nto, o l'ex\u00ecste a-o P\u00e0ize Valenci\u00e0n o con\u00e7\u00e8tto leg\u00e2le de \"predom\u00ecnio lingu\u00ecstico\" pe prom\u00eauve \u00fbnn-a de differ\u00e9nti l\u00e9ngoe ofi\u00e7i\u00e6, valen\u00e7i\u00e0n \u00f2 castegi\u00e0n, depend\u00e9ndo do terit\u00f6io. Da m\u00e6xima main\u00eaa ch'o catal\u00e0n o se d\u00ecxe valen\u00e7i\u00e0n into P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n, o spagn\u00f2llo o l'\u00e9 d\u00eeto castegi\u00e0n. Pe de ci\u00f9 e \u00e2tre l\u00e9ngoe ofi\u00e7i\u00e6, a ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte de pers\u00f3nn-e s\u00f4rde do P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n \u00fbzan a l\u00e9ngoa de s\u00e9gni valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a.\nSto p\u00e0ize chi o l'\u00e0 'na realit\u00e6 so\u00e7iolingu\u00ecstica compl\u00e8ssa e plur\u00e2le, generalm\u00e9nte co-o castegi\u00e0n scignoezz\u00e0ndo in z\u00f6ne urb\u00e0nn-e e co-o valen\u00e7i\u00e0n scignoezzando inte \u00e2ie de canp\u00e0gna e \u00e7it\u00e6 m\u00e9die.\nStoricam\u00e9nte, da-i t\u00e9npi da coloniza\u00e7i\u00f3n feod\u00e2le o valen\u00e7i\u00e0n o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to a l\u00e9ngoa de ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte do p\u00e0ize, gr\u00e0\u00e7ie \u00e0 'na l\u00eagia magior\u00e0nsa into n\u00f9mero di col\u00f2ni da Catal\u00f3gna; con l'ece\u00e7i\u00f3n de regio\u00ecn co-a front\u00eaa con Arag\u00f3nn-a (Cant\u00f3n d'Adem\u00f9s, \u00c0lto Migl\u00e0rs, \u00c0lto Pal\u00e0n\u00e7ia e Serr\u00e0ns), d\u00f3nd'i col\u00f2ni aragon\u00e9ixi, i qu\u00e6 parl\u00e0van spagn\u00f2llo, \u00earan st\u00e6ti a magior\u00e0nsa. E \u00e2tre regio\u00ecn da parl\u00e2 castegi\u00e0nn-a prez\u00e9nte (F\u00f2ia de Bogn\u00f2l, Can\u00e0l de Navarr\u00e9s, V\u00e0gle de Cofr\u00e9nts e qu\u00e0rche comm\u00f9n do Vinalop\u00f2) son o prod\u00fbto da repopola\u00e7i\u00f3n con castegi\u00e9n do s\u00e9colo XVII, dap\u00eau l'espulsci\u00f3n di mor\u00ecschi, dov\u00fbo a qu\u00e9ste g\u00e9nte ghe travagi\u00e0van a t\u00e6ra. A regi\u00f3n do B\u00e0sso Seg\u00f3ra a l'\u00e0 pat\u00eeo 'n proc\u00e8so de sostitu\u00e7i\u00f3n lingu\u00ecstica do catal\u00e0n pe-o spagn\u00f2llo into s\u00e9colo XVII dap\u00eau 'n'epidem\u00eea de p\u00e8sta into 1648 e ch'a corp\u00eco a popola\u00e7i\u00f3n da parl\u00e2 valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a A regi\u00f3n da Pl\u00e0na d'Oti\u00e9l, c\u00f3mme i comu\u00ecn de Vigl\u00e9na e Saix, az\u00f3nte a-e prov\u00ecnse inte qu\u00e6 o s'\u00f2rgan\u00eczza o P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n, che son de colt\u00fba e l\u00e9ngoa castegi\u00e0nn-a. O R\u00e9gno de Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia, donca, o no l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to 'n p\u00e0ize co-a doalit\u00e6 catal\u00e0n-spagn\u00f2lla ma catal\u00e0n-\u00e0raba inte l'et\u00e6 do m\u00eazo, co-e ece\u00e7io\u00ecn pr\u00ecmma d\u00eete.\nAnch\u00eau, inte gr\u00e9nde \u00e7it\u00e6 de regio\u00ecn da parl\u00e2 valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a (c\u00f3mme qual\u00f3nque \u00e2tre) a prez\u00e9nsa do valen\u00e7i\u00e0n a l'\u00e9 min\u00f4 pe cax\u00f3n da minoiza\u00e7i\u00f3n de qu\u00e9sta l\u00e9ngoa in fav\u00f4 do castegi\u00e0n. Segondo o PSPV (Part\u00eeo So\u00e7ial\u00ecsta do P\u00e0ize Valenci\u00e0n), a UGT (Uni\u00f3n Gener\u00e2le di Travaggi\u00e0nti), l'AVL e l'IEC, o l'\u00e9 cosc\u00ec in b\u00f3nn-a p\u00e0rte pe f\u00e2rta d'ar\u00e9nbo pol\u00ectico. De f\u00e6to, o der\u00ea scand\u00e0ggio do 2005 o m\u00f3stra che qu\u00e6xi o 37% di scand\u00e6 o l'ad\u00eauvia o valenci\u00e0n preferen\u00e7ialm\u00e9nte, int\u00e0nto che a per\u00e7ento\u00e2le a l'\u00eaa do 50% into 1995. L'\u00fbzo inte sch\u00eaue o l'\u00e9 ammerm\u00f2u asc\u00ed, anc\u00f3n e autorit\u00e6 no son ascidi\u00e6. \u00c2tre asso\u00e7ia\u00e7io\u00ecn d\u00ecxan ch'a c\u00f4rpa a l'\u00e9 do PP, o part\u00eeo pol\u00ectico ch'o gh'\u00e0 govern\u00f2u da-o 1995 a-o 2015.\nO catal\u00e0n parl\u00f2u into P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n o l'incl\u00f9dde t\u00f9tti do\u00ee dial\u00e9tti prin\u00e7ip\u00e2li do catal\u00e0n ponent\u00ecn: n\u00f6rd-occident\u00e2le e sud-occident\u00e2le. Do pr\u00ecmmo dial\u00e9tto, s\u00f4lo 'na variet\u00e6 a gh'\u00e9 parl\u00e2, o tortos\u00ecn, e s\u00f4lo inta regi\u00f3n ci\u00f9 setentrion\u00e2le. Qu\u00e9sta variet\u00e6, e o r\u00e8sto do dial\u00e9tto, a l'\u00e9 parl\u00e2 in Catal\u00f3gna e Arag\u00f3nn-a asc\u00ed. Pe de ci\u00f9, o dial\u00e9tto ocident\u00e2le o l'\u00e9 parl\u00f2u into st\u00e0to d'Andorra. Do segondo dial\u00e9tto, o s\u00f9d-ocident\u00e2le, se gh'atr\u00eauvan t\u00e0nte ci\u00f9 variet\u00e6; qu\u00e9ste son o casteglon\u00e9ngo, o valent\u00ecn, o meridion\u00e2le, o meridion\u00e2le maiorch\u00ecn e l'alacant\u00ecn da n\u00f2rd a s\u00f9d, de main\u00eaa che sto dial\u00e9tto chi o l'\u00e9 o ci\u00f9 parl\u00f2u do p\u00e0ize e, al\u00f4a, o segondo de t\u00f9tti i dial\u00e9tti catal\u00e9n. A prin\u00e7ip\u00e2le difer\u00e9nsa tra i do\u00ee dial\u00e9tti a l'\u00e9 a conioga\u00e7i\u00f3n verb\u00e2le, ci\u00f9 conserv\u00e2 e omog\u00e9nia into s\u00f9d-ocident\u00e2le, ma in c\u00e0ngio o n\u00f2rd-ocident\u00e2le o l'\u00e9 ci\u00f9 desp\u00e6gio con variet\u00e6 conserv\u00e6, evolu\u00e7io\u00ecn pr\u00f2pie \u00f2 influ\u00e9nsa do catal\u00e0n levant\u00ecn. In realt\u00e6, a variet\u00e6 st\u00e0ndar do catal\u00e0n a l'\u00e9 baz\u00e2 into dialetto \u00e7entr\u00e2le da l\u00e9ngoa, ch'o l'appart\u00eagne a-o catal\u00e0n levant\u00ecn, cosc\u00ec ch'o st\u00e0ndar ad\u00eauvi\u00f2u into P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n o l'\u00e9 adat\u00f2u.\nDivix\u00f3n aministrat\u00eeva.\nProv\u00ecnse.\nIna pr\u00ecmma divix\u00f3n da provinsa de Sp\u00e0gna s\u00f3tta dom\u00ecnio napole\u00f2nico, a-o s\u00e8colo XIX, l'amisitra\u00e7i\u00f3n spagn\u00f2lla a spart\u00ec o teri\u00f6io fra prefet\u00fbe d'Alac\u00e0nt e Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia, ch'a l'astrenz\u00e9iva co-a de Tarrag\u00f3nn-a ina l\u00ecgna ch'a l'un\u00ecva Vistab\u00e9gla e Pen\u00ecscola.\nIn 1822, pe pr\u00ecmma v\u00f2ta 'ne prov\u00ecnse c\u00f3mme le prez\u00e9nte son p\u00f2ste e spart\u00ecvan o p\u00e0ize, de n\u00f6rd a sud, in le prov\u00ecnse de Castegl\u00f3, Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia, Sci\u00e0tiva e Alac\u00e0nt. Finalm\u00e9nte, in 1833, co-a divix\u00f3n de Javier de Burgos, o n\u00f9meo o l'ar\u00e9sta in trei soprim\u00e9ndo a de Sci\u00e0tiva.\nIn 1851, s'azzont\u00e0van i terit\u00f6i castegl\u00e9n de Vigl\u00e9na \u00e0-a prov\u00ecnsa d'Alac\u00e0nt, e de Rech\u00e9na \u00e0-a de Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia. Per \u00e2tra p\u00e0rte, a comm\u00f9n st\u00f6rica valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a de Cabd\u00e9t, con t\u00f9tto ch'o av\u00e9i domand\u00f2u in 1861, a no torn\u00f2 a form\u00e2 p\u00e0rte do P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n da 1707, e a r\u00e8sta lig\u00e2 \u00e0-a prov\u00ecnsa castegl\u00e0nn-a d'Alba\u00e7\u00e9te.\nCom\u00e0rche, mancommunit\u00e6 e regio\u00ecn.\nGh'\u00e0 'na tradi\u00e7i\u00f3n b\u00e9n areix\u00e2 de comarcal\u00ecsmo, sci b\u00e9n a divix\u00f3n comarc\u00e2le prez\u00e9nte da 1970 a l'\u00e9 differ\u00e9nte da cl\u00e0scica descr\u00ecta pe Emili Be\u00fct in 1934. L'asso\u00e7ia\u00e7i\u00f3n de com\u00e0rche in qu\u00e0tro regio\u00ecn ci\u00f9 gr\u00e0nde prop\u00f2sta pe Joan Soler a no gust\u00e0va a-i pol\u00ectichi qu\u00e0nde a comunit\u00e6 out\u00f2noma a l'\u00eaa cre\u00e2 l'ann\u00f2 1982, e a s'accomod\u00f2 \u00e0-a divix\u00f3n da prov\u00ecnsa spagn\u00f2lla che z\u00e0 a l'exist\u00e9iva. Qu\u00e9ste regio\u00ecn \u00e7erc\u00e0van asso\u00e7i\u00e2 le com\u00e0rche segondo crit\u00eai st\u00f6richi, lingu\u00ecstichi e so\u00e7ioecon\u00f2michi.\nA L\u00eaze Mancommunit\u00e6 de 2018, inspi\u00e2 ina prop\u00f2sta do profes\u00f4 in dr\u00ecto aministrat\u00eevo Andr\u00e9s Boix, a d\u00e0 lib\u00e8rt\u00e6 a-e comm\u00f9n pe asso\u00e7i\u00e2se volont\u00e2iam\u00e9nte respett\u00e0ndo i conf\u00ecn comarc\u00e2li \u00f2 pe scompart\u00ee serv\u00ecxi.\nL'\u00e0nno 1999, o Cons\u00f2r\u00e7io de Com\u00e0rche \u00c7entr\u00e0le do P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n o se cr\u00e9a, co-a finalit\u00e6 de consego\u00ee 'na qu\u00e0rta prov\u00ecnsa spagn\u00f2lla. A-o mom\u00e9nto, gh'\u00e0n reconosc\u00e6 \u00e7\u00ecnque asso\u00e7ia\u00e7io\u00ecn de com\u00e0rche pe-a Generalit\u00e6 ma qu\u00e9ste regio\u00ecn no \u00e0n p\u00e9izo pol\u00ectico \u00f2 qu\u00e0rche fon\u00e7i\u00f3n aministrat\u00eeva: Com\u00e0rche do N\u00f6rd, Com\u00e0rche de D\u00e9ntro, Com\u00e0rche do T\u00f3ria-Sci\u00f3cher, Com\u00e0rche \u00c7entr\u00e0le e Com\u00e0rche do Sud.\nPol\u00ectica e gov\u00e6rno.\nO P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n, in reconoscem\u00e9nto da seu identit\u00e6 c\u00f3mme na\u00e7i\u00f3n st\u00f6rica do st\u00e0to spagnol, proveni\u00e9nte do R\u00e9gno de Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia, o l'acc\u00eade a l'aotogov\u00e6rno e o se constitu\u00ecsce in comunit\u00e6 out\u00f2noma, co-o n\u00f3mme ofi\u00e7i\u00e2 de Comunit\u00e6 Valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a, segondo o seu pr\u00ecmmmo stat\u00f3to aprov\u00f2u, o Stat\u00f3to de Madr\u00ecd, in 1982 dap\u00eau ch'o Congr\u00e8sso de los Diput\u00e0dos o rescrive o Stat\u00f3to de Benic\u00e0sim.\nT\u00f9tte e institu\u00e7io\u00ecn do gov\u00e6rno da Comunit\u00e6 Valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a cr\u00e9an a Generalit\u00e6. E prin\u00e7ip\u00e6 son: \nDe \u00e2tre institu\u00e7io\u00ecn da Generalit\u00e6 son: o Defens\u00f4 C\u00ecvico, o \u00d2rgan\u00ecximo de C\u00f3nti, o Cons\u00e9ggio Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n de Colt\u00fba, Acad\u00eamia Valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a da L\u00e9ngoa, o Cons\u00e9ggio leg\u00e2le e Consult\u00eevo e a Commisci\u00f3n Econ\u00f2mica e So\u00e7i\u00e2le.\nEconom\u00eea.\nO P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n o l'\u00e9 'n terit\u00f6io alargh\u00eeo, con 'na geograf\u00eea montagn\u00f4za e iregol\u00e2 a qu\u00e6 a l'\u00e0 f\u00e6to dif\u00edcolt\u00f4ze e comunica\u00e7io\u00ecn e o profittam\u00e9nto da t\u00e6ra, s\u00f4lo o l'\u00e0 a c\u00f2sta c\u00f3mme conesci\u00f3n con l'Eur\u00f2pa. Con in cl\u00ecmma mediterr\u00e0neo e p\u00f6ca \u00e6gua, e riz\u00f3rse natur\u00e2li do p\u00e0ize son r\u00e6e in miner\u00e2li. Gh'\u00e0 ci\u00f9 dom\u00e0nda d'\u00e6gua de quella ch'a se prod\u00fbxe, e qu\u00e9sto squil\u00ecbrio o l'\u00e9 particolam\u00e9nte s\u00e9rio a-e com\u00e0rche do sud.\nInte l'\u00e0nno 2005 o P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n o l'\u00eaa gener\u00f2u o 9,64% do PIB stat\u00e2le e a dizocupa\u00e7i\u00f3n a l'\u00eaa de 8,82%. Con t\u00f9tto che, pe-a cr\u00eexi mondi\u00e2le do 2008, a dizocupa\u00e7i\u00f3n a l'\u00e0 mont\u00e2 f\u00ecn a-o 23% da popola\u00e7i\u00f3n att\u00eeva inte l'\u00e0nno 2010. Pe quante l'\u00e0 da f\u00e2 e rizorse um\u00e0nn-e, l'ocupa\u00e7i\u00f3n a l'\u00eaa ariv\u00e2 a-o 58,64% do tot\u00e2le into 2005, scib\u00e9n ch'e diferense de z\u00e9nne \u00eaan ciut\u00f2sto accaxon\u00e6. O mod\u00e9llo d'attivit\u00e6 comer\u00e7i\u00e2 valen\u00e7i\u00e0n carater\u00ecstico o l'\u00e9 Pic\u00ecnn-e e M\u00e9die Impr\u00e9ize (PMI), pe-a ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte de famiggia, con t\u00f9tto che gh'\u00e9 di multina\u00e7ion\u00e2li. Asc\u00ec b\u00e9n ch'o l'\u00e0 pat\u00eco a gr\u00e9ive cr\u00eexi tra o 1973 e o 1985, into prez\u00e9nte o l'\u00e9 a segonda outonom\u00eea esportat\u00f4a do st\u00e0to con in vol\u00f9mme d'esporta\u00e7io\u00ecn \u00e7\u00e8rnegi\u00f2u in 16,910 mio\u00ecn d'\u00e9uro inte l'\u00e0nno 2005.\nDemograf\u00eea.\nA popola\u00e7i\u00f3n stim\u00e2 pe l'Instit\u00fbto Na\u00e7ion\u00e2le de Stat\u00ecstica (INE) a-o primmo de zen\u00e2 do 2013 a l'\u00eaa de 5,104,365 pers\u00f3nn-e. A demograf\u00eea do P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n a l'\u00eaa st\u00e6ta con\u00e7entr\u00e2 in comm\u00f9n e z\u00f6ne cortiv\u00e6 a-a z\u00ecnn-a di sci\u00f9mmi ci\u00f9 import\u00e0nti (Sci\u00f3cher, T\u00f3ria, Seg\u00f3ra, Vinalop\u00f3), cosc\u00ec c\u00f3mme in popola\u00e7io\u00ecn da c\u00f2sta co-in p\u00f2rto import\u00e0nte. E popola\u00e7io\u00ecn ci\u00f9 import\u00e0nte s'atr\u00eauvan inte l'\u00e2ia metropolit\u00e0nn-a de Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia, o corid\u00f4 tra Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia e Castegl\u00f3 de la Plana e o corid\u00f4 tra \u00c8lx e Alac\u00e0nt.\nDe qu\u00e9sta distribu\u00e7i\u00f3n tradi\u00e7ion\u00e2le a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to \u00f2rigin\u00e2 pe-e carater\u00ecstiche gi\u00f6gr\u00e0fiche e a poscibilit\u00e6 d'iriga\u00e7i\u00f3n, \u00fbn o l'acap\u00ecsce ch'a denscit\u00e6 de popola\u00e7i\u00f3n a l'\u00e9 magi\u00f4 inte com\u00e0rche \u00e7entr\u00e2le e do sud, e min\u00f4 inte com\u00e0rche do n\u00f2rd e de l'entrot\u00e6ra. A gr\u00e0nde ativit\u00e6 industri\u00e2le e di prod\u00fbti agr\u00eccoli a l'\u00e0 influens\u00f2u a demograf\u00eea asc\u00ec, inte \u00e7it\u00e6 de l'entrot\u00e6ra c\u00f3mme Alc\u00f2i, \u00c9lda, Nov\u00e9lda, Ontign\u00e9nt, Petr\u00e9r, Vigl\u00e9na e a V\u00e0gl d'Usci\u00f3.\nInti \u00fbrtimi \u00e0nni, a con\u00e7entra\u00e7i\u00f3n a s'\u00e8 acento\u00e2 inti gr\u00e0ndi \u00e7it\u00e6 e e seu \u00e2ie metropolit\u00e0nn-e (ne res\u00e2tan Tor\u00e9nt, Misl\u00e0ta, Pat\u00e8rna, Borgias\u00f2t, S\u00e0nt Vi\u00e7\u00e8nt del Rasp\u00e9ig, etc.) e, particolam\u00e9nte, vil\u00e0ggi e \u00e7it\u00e6 da c\u00f2sta. Cosc\u00ec, vil\u00e0ggi tradi\u00e7ionalm\u00e9nte pic\u00ecn c\u00f3mme Benid\u00f2rm \u00f2 Torev\u00e9gla \u00e0n pat\u00eeo 'n aum\u00e9nto not\u00e9vole dov\u00fbo a-e migra\u00e7io\u00ecn provoch\u00e6 pe-o tur\u00ecsmo, anc\u00f3n ci\u00f9 not\u00e9vole int'i m\u00e9ixi da st\u00e6.\nSe peu d\u00ee, donca, ch'a demograf\u00eea do P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n a-a giorn\u00e2 d'ancheu a l'\u00e9 z\u00e0 pe-a ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte urb\u00e0nn-a, con t\u00e0nta influ\u00e9nsa de migra\u00e7io\u00ecn staxon\u00e6 e pe-o tur\u00ecsmo, prin\u00e7ipalm\u00e9nte v\u00e8rso i vil\u00e0ggi da c\u00f2sta.\nColt\u00fba e tradi\u00e7io\u00ecn.\nI atrib\u00fbti coltu\u00e2li valen\u00e7i\u00e9n son, int'in m\u00f2ddo ci\u00e6o, mediterr\u00e0nei pe raxo\u00ecn gi\u00f6gr\u00e0fiche e st\u00f6riche con influ\u00e9nse de t\u00f9tti i p\u00f2poli che gh'\u00e0n intervegn\u00fbo. A religi\u00f3n cat\u00f2lica, anc\u00f3n co-a ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte di cred\u00e9nti, a l'\u00e0 march\u00e6 e carater\u00ecstiche individo\u00e2le e de t\u00f9tti, asc\u00ec.\nScib\u00e9n t\u00e0nte tradi\u00e7io\u00ecn ant\u00eeghe p\u00eauan av\u00e9i 'n'\u00f2r\u00ecgine rom\u00e2na (c\u00f3mm'o c\u00f9lto a-o f\u00eaugo \u00f2 a di\u00eata) da m\u00e6xima main\u00eaa ch'\u00e2tri l\u00eaughi do Mediterr\u00e0neo, gh'\u00e9 anche di import\u00e0nti influ\u00e9nse \u00e0rabe inta colt\u00fba, prin\u00e7ipalm\u00e9nte inta gastronom\u00eea.\nDa conqu\u00ecsta feod\u00e2le, anc\u00f3n anch\u00eau l'\u00e9 vixibile e diferense coltu\u00e6 tra i vil\u00e0ggi de repopola\u00e7i\u00f3n catal\u00e0nn-a, aragon\u00e9ize (ciam\u00e6 \"xurros\") e de Cast\u00e9gia.\nDe qu\u00e9ste tradi\u00e7io\u00ecn coltu\u00e6 se p\u00eau \u00e7it\u00e2 generalm\u00e9nte:\nSp\u00f6rt.\nO sp\u00f6rt tradi\u00e7ion\u00e2le pe e\u00e7el\u00e9nsa o l'\u00e9 a b\u00e0la valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a, f\u00ecn a-o p\u00f3nto d'av\u00e9i zugo\u00e9i profescion\u00e6 e 'na squ\u00e0dra valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a de b\u00e0la ch'a parte\u00e7\u00ecpa inte conpeti\u00e7io\u00ecn interna\u00e7ion\u00e2le ci\u00f9 import\u00e0nte. Qu\u00e9sto sp\u00f6rt o l'\u00e9 pratic\u00f2u in ci\u00f9 de \u00eautto modalit\u00e6, b\u00e9n a-a str\u00e2 b\u00e9n in un \"trinquet\". Int'inc\u00f3ntri, o l'\u00e9 t\u00ecpico ch'o p\u00f9brico o s'atr\u00eauve qu\u00e6xi invad\u00e9ndo o sp\u00e0\u00e7io de z\u00eaugo e a prez\u00e9nsa d'un \u00f2 do\u00ee \"marxadors\" arecug\u00e9ndo e scom\u00ecse pe ciasched\u00f9nn-a de squ\u00e0ddre. S\u00f4lo s'ad\u00eauvian do\u00ee c\u00f4, pe de ci\u00f9 o gi\u00e0nco, o bl\u00eau e o r\u00f3sso pe-e braghe e e espardille. A pr\u00e0ttica e conosc\u00e9nsa de qu\u00e9sto sp\u00f6rt a monta co-i inc\u00f3ntri retrasm\u00ecssi pe TV e i n\u00eauvi instit\u00fbti d'educa\u00e7i\u00f3n che gh'\u00e0n di piste pe zug\u00e2.\nUnn-a \u00e2tra ativit\u00e6 b\u00e9n carater\u00ecstica a l'\u00e9 a combicolt\u00fba, \u00f2 c\u00f3mbi sp\u00f6rt\u00eevi, 'na prattic\u00e2 comen\u00e7\u00e2 inti \u00e0nni 20. L'\u00e9 tradi\u00e7ion\u00e2le asc\u00ec o z\u00eaugo da \"petanca\", unn-a sp\u00eace de b\u00f2cce.\nMa o sp\u00f6rt ci\u00f9 popol\u00e2, c\u00f3mme in qu\u00e6xi t\u00f9tto o pian\u00eata, o l'\u00e9 o z\u00eaugo do bal\u00f3n. A-o P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n gh'\u00e9 de squ\u00e0ddre import\u00e0nti de bal\u00f3n: o Val\u00e8ncia CF, o Villarreal CF, o Levante UE (o ci\u00f9 ant\u00eego, fond\u00f2u into 1909), l'Elche CF, l'H\u00e9rcules CF, o Castell\u00f3 CF e o CE Alcoi\u00e0. Un \u00e2tro sp\u00f6rt ol\u00ecmpico resalt\u00f2u o l'\u00e9 o b\u00e0sket, co-e squ\u00e0ddre Val\u00e8ncia B\u00e0squet e Etosa Alacant. O sp\u00f6rt femen\u00ecn ci\u00f9 popol\u00e6 o l'\u00e9 l'h\u00e0nb\u00f2l, into qu\u00e6 e squ\u00e0ddre z\u00e0 scent\u00e6 de Balonmano Mar Sagunto e Club Balonmano Calpisa \u00e0n guagn\u00f2u numer\u00f4xi t\u00ectoli import\u00e0nti.\nO p\u00e0ize o l'\u00e0 anche o fam\u00f4zo circo\u00ecto de X\u00e8st, con ci\u00f9 de 4.000 m\u00eatri pe g\u00eeo, donde se f\u00e0 o Gr\u00e0n Pr\u00e9mio da Comunit\u00e6 Valen\u00e7i\u00e0nn-a inte discipl\u00ecnn-e de motocicl\u00ecsmo, MotoGP e Superbike inte l'\u00fbrtima giorn\u00e2 do Canpion\u00f2u do M\u00f3ndo de motocicl\u00ecsmo. Qu\u00e9sto circo\u00ecto o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to in\u00f6gu\u00f2u o 19 de set\u00e9nbre do 1999 e o se ci\u00e0mma \u201cRicardo Tormo\u201d, in \u00f2m\u00e0gio p\u00f2stumo a-o pil\u00f2tto valen\u00e7i\u00e0n. O circo\u00ecto o l'\u00e0 65000 car\u00eaghe e capa\u00e7it\u00e6 pe 120.000 pers\u00f3nn-e, p\u00f6cas\u00e6.\nL'\u00e0nno 2008, o Gr\u00e0nde Pr\u00e9mio d'Eur\u00f2pa o se comen\u00e7\u00e0va a \u00e7elebr\u00e2 con p\u00ecche da Formula 1, GP 2, Formula 3, Formula BMW e Porsche Mobil 1 Supercup into Circo\u00ecto Urb\u00e0n de Val\u00e9n\u00e7ia. Qu\u00e9sto circo\u00ecto o l'\u00e0 5.473 m\u00eatri pe g\u00eeo e capa\u00e7it\u00e6 pe 110.000 spetato\u00ee distribu\u00ee in 23 scain\u00e6. O gr\u00e0nde pr\u00e9mio av\u00e9iva de sup\u00f3ne un inp\u00e0to econ\u00f2mico de 70 mio\u00ecn d'euri a l'\u00e0nno, ma no o s'ad\u00eauvia da 2013 e a infrastrut\u00fba a se pon\u00e9iva in c\u00e6ga o 2017.\nF\u00e8ste.\nE f\u00e8ste ci\u00f9 renom\u00e6 a livello interna\u00e7ion\u00e2le e ci\u00f9 import\u00e0nti do P\u00e0ize Valen\u00e7i\u00e0n son:\nGastronom\u00eea.\nA gastronom\u00eea a l'\u00e9 marc\u00e2 pe-a gi\u00f6graf\u00eea do p\u00e0ize. Cosc\u00ec, a-a c\u00f2sta res\u00e2tan e \"coques\" (t\u00f2rti e fug\u00e0se) e i t\u00f3ndi de \u00e7ere\u00e2le (r\u00eezo, gr\u00e0n, gran\u00f3n), leg\u00f9mi, fr\u00fbta (\u00fbga, \u00e7etr\u00f3n) e \u00e2tri \u00f2rt\u00e0gi; ma in c\u00e0ngio a d\u00e9ntro res\u00e2tan a produ\u00e7i\u00f3n de n\u00f4xe, am\u00e0ndoa, lug\u00e0nega, t\u00f3ndi c\u00f3mm'o gasp\u00e0cio \u00f2 e pugn\u00e0te, e prod\u00fbti de c\u00e0ccia. E contribo\u00e7io\u00ecn gr\u00eaghe, rom\u00e0nn-e, mosulm\u00e0nn-e e cresti\u00e0nn-e ci\u00f9 not\u00e9vole son, respet\u00eevam\u00e9nte: l'am\u00e0ndoa e o v\u00ecn; l'\u00f2rz\u00e2 e l'\u00eauio d'o\u00eeva; o tor\u00f3n, i frisc\u00e9u, o \"arnad\u00ed\" e \u00e2tre d\u00f4\u00e7e; a \"sobrassada\", i besch\u00e9utti e o \"espencat\"."}
{"id": "30180", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=30180", "title": "Sccium\u00eaa Varatella", "text": "A sccium\u00eaa Varatella (anche sulu A Sccium\u00eaa, \"Scciumaira Varatella\" in carporu) a l'\u00e8 in scciumme, lungu circa sette chilometri, ch'u nasce dunde se unisce u Ri\u00e0n de C\u00e2rpe cu-u Ri\u00e0n da Valle e ch'u sf\u00f6ccia intu M\u00e2 Ligure.\nGeograf\u00eca.\nPercursu.\nU scciumme Varatella u se furma circa au centru du propiu bac\u00ecn, a l'altessa de 170 metri in s'ou livellu du m\u00e2 inta regi\u00f9n d\u00ecta du S\u00e2tu du L\u00fc (\"S\u00e4tu du L\u00fcvu\" in carporu), intu teritoriu du cum\u00fcn de Tui\u00e0n. Chi a gh'\u00e8 infatti a conflensa di dui scciummi ch'i dan urigine aa Varatella, sai\u00e8 a di u Ri\u00e0n de C\u00e2rpe e u Ri\u00e0n da Valle. Vix\u00ecn au centru storicu de Tui\u00e0n, a ina qu\u00f6ta de 45 metri in s'ou livellu du m\u00e2, u Varatella u ris\u00eave l'\u00e8gua dau s\u00f2 prinsip\u00e2le afluente, u Ri\u00e0n Baresci\u00f9n, ch'u r\u00ecva daa valle da Baestr\u00ecn.\nIntr\u00e0u inta ciana cost\u00eaa du Burghettu, u procedde in moddo qu\u00e8xi rettilineu fina aa costa, dunde u sf\u00f6ccia intu M\u00e2 Ligure.\nAfluenti.\nU ri\u00e0n Varatella u l'\u00e8 cunscider\u00e0u de quintu de urdine, d\u00e2tu ch'u l'\u00e8 gener\u00e0u da l'uni\u00f9n de dui scciummi (u Ri\u00e0n de C\u00e2rpe e u Ri\u00e0n da Valle) de quartu urdine, graddu au qu\u00e2le u r\u00ecva anche u Ri\u00e0n de Baresci\u00f9n. Pertantu u bac\u00ecn du Varatella u se p\u00f6 cunscider\u00e2 cumme l'uni\u00f9n de trei sutta-bac\u00ecn di ri\u00e8 mensun\u00e8 de d'\u00e2tu.\nPartindu da munte, in s'ou l\u00e2tu sinistru u Varatella u ris\u00eave i seguenti afluenti:\nInvece, in sa destra du Varatella, u gh'\u00e8 i seguenti afluenti:\nBac\u00ecn idrugraficu\nU bac\u00ecn idrugraficu du turente Varatella u se larga inte ina vasta z\u00f6na, d\u00e2tu u gran n\u00fcmeru de afluenti ch'i se caccia inta sccium\u00eaa. In particul\u00e2re u so bac\u00ecn u se svil\u00fcppa inti teritori di cum\u00fcn du Burghettu, de Tui\u00e0n, de Buis\u00e0n, de Baestr\u00ecn, de Castelveggiu e, pe ina p\u00e2rte picina, anche du Sej\u00e2. Stu bac\u00ecn, orient\u00e0u in diresi\u00f9n nord-ovest/sud-est, u l'\u00e0 ina superfice tut\u00e2le de pocu ci\u00fc picina de 44\u00a0km2 e in perimetru lungu 25\u00a0km.\nU bac\u00ecn du Varatella u l'\u00e8 separ\u00e0u da quelli cunfinanti da ina serie de munti e de culine:\nDau puntu de vista da s\u00f2 geulugia, u bac\u00ecn du Varatella u l'\u00e8 divisu inte tr\u00e8 p\u00e2rte tantu diferenti: a p\u00e2rte muntagnusa tra Tui\u00e0n e C\u00e2rpe a l'\u00e8 furm\u00e2 prinsip\u00e2lmente da rocce ricche de calc\u00e2re e dulomie, ch'i crea in paesaggiu aridu, cun tanti rivass\u00f9i e p\u00ecn de grotte e g\u00e2rbi in se r\u00ecve di munti.\nL'\u00e2tra p\u00e2rte de munti, in particul\u00e2re inti cum\u00fcn de Buis\u00e0n e Baestr\u00ecn, a l'\u00e8 carateriz\u00e2 da ina magi\u00f9 presensa de scistu, ch'a l'\u00e0 purt\u00e0u a paesaggi ci\u00fc \"levigh\u00e8\" e menu aridi. Aa f\u00ecn, a p\u00e2rte de cian\u00fca custea a l'\u00e8 u risult\u00e2tu de milenni d'am\u00fcggiu de materi\u00e2le purt\u00e0u a valle dau Varatella e a curispunde ai \u00fcrtimi 4 km du percursu da sccium\u00eaa, dau centru de Tui\u00e0n fina aa s\u00f2 fuxe.\nEcunum\u00eca.\nA desp\u00eatu de in \u00fczu urm\u00e2i limit\u00e0u aa sula irigasi\u00f9n, quande nu se va a truv\u00e2 inte \u00fcn di frequenti mumenti de secca, intu pas\u00e0u a presensa da sccium\u00eaa a l'\u00eaa fundament\u00e2le e muture pe l'intr\u00eaga ecunumia di paisi du Burghettu e de Tui\u00e0n ultre che, cunsciderandu anche i s\u00f2 afluenti, de Baestr\u00ecn e de C\u00e2rpe asc\u00ec. Prinsipalmente l'\u00e8gua du Varatella a vegn\u00ecva utiliz\u00e2 cumme fursa mutrixe pe-i tanti mu\u00ecn e gunbi custru\u00eci lungu e s\u00f2 r\u00ecve, ultre che pe aliment\u00e2 u scist\u00eama de irigasi\u00f9n luc\u00e2le.\nCumensandu dai gunbi, quellu ci\u00fc a munte u l'\u00eaa quellu de C\u00e2rpe. Scitu\u00e0u in sa muderna stradda pruvinci\u00e2le, u l'utiliz\u00e2va l'\u00e8gua du Ri\u00e0n de C\u00e2rpe pe mesci\u00e2, in casc\u00e2ta, e s\u00f2 due m\u00f6e: a primma a asiun\u00e2va u mu\u00ecn du paise, invece a segunda a l'\u00eaa quella du gunbu. Ben ci\u00fc a valle, in po' ci\u00fc in s\u00fc du punte da pruvinci\u00e2le pe Buis\u00e0n, se truv\u00e2va invece u cusc\u00ec d\u00ectu gunbu da Urpe, du qu\u00e2le u se p\u00f6 ancua vegghe l'edifissiu, e p\u00f6 u gunbu de Tr\u00e8nne, in lucalit\u00e8 Braia e caci\u00e0u s\u00fc intu cursu du bunbardamentu ale\u00e0u de Tui\u00e0n du 12 agustu du '44. Cuntinuandu a chin\u00e2 lungu u cursu da sccium\u00eaa se incuntr\u00e2van ancua u gunbu da Cum\u00fcna, de propiet\u00e8 p\u00fcblica e scitu\u00e0u vix\u00ecn au cusc\u00ec d\u00ectu punte de Gi\u00e8re (\"punte de Giaire\" in tuiran\u00ecn); d'anc\u00f6 demol\u00ecu e vix\u00ecn au qu\u00e2le u se truv\u00e2va ina lunga vasca uz\u00e2 pe lav\u00e2 a sansa.\nGh'\u00eaa p\u00f6 u gunbu du Pierluigi, ci\u00fc o menu a l'altessa de l'atuale circulu du tenni de Tui\u00e0n, e u grande gunbu de Bresci\u00e0n, de propiet\u00e8 de l'omonima famiggia burghese du Burghettu e scitu\u00e0u esattamente in s'ou cunf\u00ecn tra Tui\u00e0n e u Burghettu. Drentu a l'abit\u00e0u de Tui\u00e0n, aliment\u00e0u per\u00f2 da l'\u00e8gua du Ri\u00e0n Baresci\u00f9n, u se truv\u00e2va l'\u00fcrtimu gunbu a \u00e8gua du paise. Inta cian\u00fca cust\u00eaa, pe cuntru, u paise du Burghettu u l'\u00eaa du t\u00fcttu sensa gunbi, ma a ogni moddu u l'ax\u00eava ina prudusi\u00f9n de ouvive ci\u00fc cuntegn\u00fca.\nUltre che pe mesci\u00e2 e m\u00f6e di gunbi, l'\u00e8gua du Varatella a l'aliment\u00e2va in estesu scist\u00eama de bei, specialmente inta p\u00e2rte mediu-\u00e2ta du s\u00f2 cursu. Partindu da munte, u primmu beu ch'u se incuntr\u00e2va u l'\u00e8 quellu ch'u gj\u00e2va l'\u00e8gua daa lucalit\u00e8 S\u00e2tu du L\u00fc, scurendu lungu a spunda sinistra da sccium\u00eaa fina a ariv\u00e2 ae cusc\u00ec d\u00ecte C\u00e0 de Cr\u00e2ve, dunde u l'aliment\u00e2va in'ant\u00ecga cart\u00eaa p\u00f6 riadat\u00e2 a abitasi\u00f9n e d'anc\u00f6 abandun\u00e2. In regi\u00f9n Martinettu u se ne truv\u00e2va \u00e2tri dui: u primmu u l'aliment\u00e2va l'uficina du Fer\u00e2 (da \u00fcrtimu, Briossu) invece u segundu, d'urigine ci\u00fc ant\u00ecga cumme quellu de C\u00e0 de Cr\u00e2ve esendu arm\u00eanu du settesentu, u pas\u00e2va pe-e c\u00e0 anc\u00f6 abandun\u00e8 da lucalit\u00e8 Martinettu e, cun l'avert\u00fca da vixina c\u00e2va, u vegn\u00ecva utiliz\u00e0u pe aliment\u00e0 u mu\u00ecn ch'u maxin\u00e2va e pr\u00ece chi estr\u00e8te in gi\u00e8a. U beu du fer\u00e2 u ne aliment\u00e2va p\u00f6 in \u00e2tru, uz\u00e0u pe cuntru pe l'irigasi\u00f9n di ter\u00e9n tra u Varatella e a costa de D\u00e2ri e ch'u pas\u00e2va sutta au punte pe Buis\u00e0n. Pe fin\u00ec, u ci\u00fc grossu pe purt\u00e2 e estensci\u00f9n, u gh'\u00eaa ancua u cusc\u00ec d\u00ectu beu de l'\u00e8gua c\u00e2da (\"beu de l'\u00e4iva c\u00e4da\" in tuiran\u00ecn), ciam\u00e0u cusc\u00ec daa tenperat\u00fca de l'\u00e8gua de surgente ch'u l'atravers\u00e2va. Stu beu, ultre a purt\u00e2 l'\u00e8gua pe l'irigasi\u00f9n, u l'asiun\u00e2va anche i gunbi du Pierluigi e de Bresci\u00e0n. Da chi u ne aliment\u00e2va in \u00e2tru, ch'u cur\u00ecva l\u00fcngu l'atuale pruvinci\u00e2le pe-u Burghettu (ciam\u00e0u \"beu du Cian du Beve\u00e4iva\", in tuiran\u00ecn), inte ina canaletta a l'internu da mi\u00e2gia che a resse, arivandu fina a l'altessa de l'atuale reunda pe-u svinculu de l'autustradda, pe cunsundise aa f\u00ecn intu Varatella.\nComunicasi\u00f9i.\nAntigamente inta p\u00e2rte bassa du cursu du Varatella u nu ghe n'\u00e8 m\u00e2i st\u00e8tu de punti, cu-u diffisile atraversamentu du turente ch'u l'avegn\u00ecva sulu in di guadi a l'internu du s\u00f2 lettu. Pe cuntru u vix\u00ecn Ri\u00e0n Casasse, in s'ou cunf\u00ecn cun L\u00f6a, u l'\u00e8 da lungu tenpu dut\u00e0u de propi atraversamenti, cumme testimuni\u00e0u dau cusc\u00ec d\u00ectu \"Puntassu\". Quest'opera, che a risale ai tenpi di rum\u00e2ni, \u00e0ua a l'\u00e8 in p\u00e2rte inter\u00e2 ma ancua visibile in sa r\u00ecva sinistra du ri\u00e0n, che intu frattenpu, u l'\u00e0 mudific\u00e0u u s\u00f2 cursu.\nA situasi\u00f9n a l'\u00e8 invece diferente intu toccu du Varatella ci\u00fc versu munte dunde, grasie aa ci\u00fc poca larghessa du turente, i sun st\u00e8ti custru\u00eci vari punti sa in tenpi storici. Tra sti l\u00ec, a strut\u00fca ci\u00fc notevole a l'\u00e8 seg\u00fcamente quella du cusc\u00ec d\u00ectu punte \"de Giaire\" (sai\u00e8 a d\u00ec de gi\u00e8re, in tuiran\u00ecn), ch'u l'\u00e0 tr\u00e8 arch\u00e8 a t\u00fcttu sestu e ch'u l'\u00e8 st\u00e8tu custru\u00ecu intu XIII seculu. Tra i punti dut\u00e8 de in sertu pr\u00eaxu architetonicu i se regurda ancua quellu, senpre a Tui\u00e0n, lungu a v\u00eagia stradda ch'a purta aa Certussa, vix\u00ecn au vegiu mu\u00ecn cumun\u00e2le du beu \"de l'\u00e4iva c\u00e4da\". Stu punte, daa strut\u00fca a due arch\u00e8, u l'\u00e8 cunusci\u00fcu, d\u00e2ta a s\u00f2 pusisi\u00f9n, cumme u punte \"du murin\". Pocu doppu a confluensa tra u Ri\u00e0n de C\u00e2rpe e u Ri\u00e0n da Valle, in teritoriu carporu, u se tr\u00f6va p\u00f6 u cusc\u00ec punte du Sergente, in sa v\u00eagia stradda che a culeg\u00e2va l'ecs cum\u00fcn cu-a riv\u00eaa, inest\u00e2 pocu ci\u00fc in bassu de l'ant\u00ecga Via da Valle. Lungu a stessa via, ci\u00fc a m\u00e2, se tr\u00f6va ancua di punti pic\u00ecn ch'i l'\u00eaa au servisiu de ant\u00ecghe fabriche in lucalit\u00e8 Martinettu, cumme quellu da cart\u00eaa e quellu du fer\u00e2.\nIn tenpi ci\u00fc muderni sun st\u00e8ti realiz\u00e8, ci\u00fc o menu inte l'urdine, u viadottu da feruv\u00eca Z\u00eana-Vintimiggia, inaugur\u00e2 intu 1872, quellu de l'Aurelia e quellu da pruvinci\u00e2le pe Buis\u00e0n, che a l'inisiu a l'\u00eaa in senplice sent\u00e9. Opera ingegneristica nutevuliscima pe-a z\u00f6na intr\u00eaga a l'\u00e8 p\u00f6 st\u00e8ta a custrusi\u00f9n, tra u 1913 e u 1926, de l'\u00e2tu Punte Maineru in lucalit\u00e8 S\u00e2tu du L\u00fc, realis\u00e0u inte l'ocax\u00f9n da custrusi\u00f9n da stradda Tui\u00e0n-C\u00e2rpe (l'avert\u00fca du toccu C\u00e2rpe-Barden\u00eai a l'\u00e8 infatti ci\u00fc muderna). A ogni moddu, stu viadottu u nu presenta ci\u00fc a s\u00f2 strut\u00fca urigin\u00e2le, esendu st\u00e8tu custru\u00ecu pe due otte intu doppugu\u00e8ra: doppu \u00ease st\u00e8tu demul\u00ecu dai partig\u00e8 intu 1944, a sucesiva ricustrusi\u00f9n a s'\u00e8 rivel\u00e2 prublematica, rendendu neces\u00e2iu in n\u00f6vu rifacimentu de l'opera. Realiz\u00e8 in tenpi ci\u00fc recenti i sun p\u00f6 u punte du lungum\u00e2, quellu de Via Leonardo da Vinci, u Viadottu Varatella de l'Autustradda Z\u00eana-Vintimiggia e quellu du suttustante svinculu."}
